Product description

The 3-Stripes mean heritage. And when they're placed on these adidas Grand Court Alpha shoes, they celebrate generations of originality. The clean silhouette brings forth that timeless look. An embossed logo on the tongue and upscale stitchwork give everything a modern touch. Cloudfoam brings cushioning that keeps every step a pampered experience.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
